                        </label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="quiz-question">
                    <h4>5. What is the minimum processor requirement for Windows 11 24H2?</h4>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <label class="quiz-option">
                            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="7gen"> Intel 7th generation
                        </label>
                        <label class="quiz-option">
                            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="8gen"> Intel 8th generation with SSE4.2 support
                        </label>
